properties.description: The Zebras Hub is a safe space in the heart of Brandon, Suffolk. Situated at the Harvey Adam Centre on the industrial estate, we run many services from the hub; including our weekly Friday coffee morning which is FREE and open from 11am -1pm each week. This is open to our whole community to attend. We additionally run other services such as our SEND parents space and other special events throughout the year.
properties.title: Zebras Hub Brandon
